Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.83,0:16:24.07,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\pos(960,835)}每次航天器做了一个去饱和机动\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}Each time the vehicle did a desaturation maneuver,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.29,0:16:27.61,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\pos(960,835)}它记录它的做了什么 并报告回地球\N{\r1080P-src-hans-sans-Bold-50\blur4}it recorded what it did and reported it back down to earth
